name: Super 8 In 1
overview: 8-in-1 pirate compilation. As with most pirates, it is full of poor spelling on the label. It contains this games: Super Mario Land IV (Super Mario World) To Gear (Top Gear) Joe & Mack Super Cup Soccer (Super Soccer?) Tom & Jerry F1-Zero (F-Zero) October Hunter (Hunt for Red October) Hit The Ice Other version contains Bomber Man Home Alone 2 Lamborghini American (Challenge) Magic Boy Super Mario World Pit Fighter Tom & Jerry Universal Soldier
